♪The moon's reflection in the water♪

7
00:00:26,100 --> 00:00:27,620
♪Never shattered♪

8
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:31,220
♪That beautiful lie♪

9
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:36,950
♪Perhaps I'd never have understood♪

10
